/*
  Socket.IO client placeholder.

  Why this exists:
  - If your network blocks CDNs, the chat UI can fail because io() is undefined.
  - You can download the real Socket.IO browser bundle and replace THIS file.

  Recommended replacement command (run from the project root):

    mkdir -p static/vendor
    curl -L "https://cdn.socket.io/4.5.0/socket.io.min.js" -o static/vendor/socket.io.min.js

  After replacing, hard-refresh the browser (Ctrl+Shift+R).
*/
